headline: An Astrologer for the Internet Era
abstract: Chani Nicholas doesnâ€™t want to tell you who you are, but who you can be.
lead_paragraph: The first time I met up with the astrologer Chani Nicholas in Los Angeles, in December, it was for a lunch interview. We sipped our drinks and chewed truffle French fries; I asked questions and she answered them. The conversation flowed easily. We laughed a lot.
